    refactor: ALL 8 brains now use direct function calls ΓÇö ZERO HTTP-to-localhost
    
    Every brain domain extracted into core/services/:
    
      core/services/chat_service.py    ΓÇö list/create/get/delete/history/send via DB
      core/services/files_service.py   ΓÇö tree/browse/read/write/create/delete via Path
      core/services/govern_service.py  ΓÇö dashboard/approvals/rules/persona/genesis via DB+FS
      core/services/data_service.py    ΓÇö api_sources/web_sources/stats via JSON files
      core/services/tasks_service.py   ΓÇö live/history/submit/scheduled/time_sense via DB+FS
      core/services/code_service.py    ΓÇö projects/tree/read/write/generate via Path+LLM
      core/services/system_service.py  ΓÇö runtime/health/hot_reload/diagnostics (already done)
      core/services/chat_service.py    ΓÇö consensus via cognitive.consensus_engine (already done)
    
    Before: 78 HTTP-to-localhost calls (requests.get/post to self)
